content.rendered:
Directed by Manish Gupta

Written by Manish Gupta

Cast Rohan Mehra (Birbal Choudhary). Vinay Pathak (Bansi Keswani). Ranvir Shorey (Jamshed Ji). Gul Panag (Pooja Keswani). Arif Zakaria (Sinha). Nishit Broker (Randhir). Vidhi Chitalia (Manali). Siddhesh Deshmukh (Slum guy 1). Hemant K Gaur (Slum Guy (as Hemant k Gaur)). Ashish Gokhale(Aslekar). Sanjay Gurbaxani (Judge R. Mistry). Madhvendra Jha (CBI Inspector Kamath). Muskaan Khubchandani (Ayesha). Akash Sinha (Suresh). Shivraj Walvekar (Mazumdar)

Language Hindi

Producers Manish Gupta. Rajesh Kejriwal. Gurpal Sachar

Production Kyoorius Digital. Zee Studios
